{"lemma":"دَرَنُ","slug":"دَرَنُ","root":"د.ر.ن","root_slug":"د-ر-ن","root_link":"/words/roots/د-ر-ن","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":1,"pos_tags":["verb"],"has_etymology":false,"sense_count":0},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n12479","n12481","n12483","n12482"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AF%D9%8E%D8%B1%D9%8E%D9%86%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n12479","headword_ar":"دَرِنَ","root":"drn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daranN","text_ar":"دَرَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, * S, * M, Msb, K; *) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Adrn","text_ar":"ادرن","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (T, M, K;)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a garment, S, M, &c.)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, dirty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filthy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, defiled, polluted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smeared, with dirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darinato yaduhu biAl$~aYo'i","text_ar":"دَرِنَتْ يَدُهُ بِالشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His hand was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, defiled, polluted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smeared, with the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K"]},{"entry_id":"n12481","headword_ar":"دَرَنٌ","root":"drn","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dirtiness,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filthiness;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defilement,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pollution, with dirt"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(T, K:) and accord. to the K, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_idorawonN","text_ar":"الاـِدْرَوْنٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also is syn. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aranu","text_ar":"الدَّرَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; but ISd says that this is not known. (So in the TA. [In the text of the M, however, as given in the TT, in the place of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aranu","text_ar":"الدَّرَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"in this case I find"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlradiY=","text_ar":"الرَدِى="},{"kind":"text","text":"(for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alr~adiYo'u","text_ar":"الرَّدِىْءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the bad,"},{"kind":"text","text":"&c.); and another passage in the M, respecting a signification of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_idorawonN","text_ar":"اـِدْرَوْنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (which see below,) suggests that the explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA_idorawonu","text_ar":"الاـِدْرَوْنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"as meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~aranu","text_ar":"الدَّرَنُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"may have been taken from this passage in consequence of an oversight.])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maAkaAna","text_ar":"مَاكَانَ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A_il~aA kadaranK bikaf~iY","text_ar":"اـِلَّا كَدَرَنٍ بِكَفِّى"},{"kind":"text","text":", meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It was no otherwise than like dirt in my hand,"},{"kind":"text","text":"which I therefore wiped with the other hand, is a prov. applied in the case of a thing done in haste. (M.) ―         -b2-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^um~u daranK","text_ar":"اُمُّ دَرَنٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The present world,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the present state of existence."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Z, K.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daranN","text_ar":"دَرَنٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used as meaning (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Vileness, ignominy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"abjectness."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Har p. 509.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","K","T"]},{"entry_id":"n12483","headword_ar":"دَرَنٌ","root":"drn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"saHaAbN","text_ar":"سَحَابٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,) or ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dar~aAnN","text_ar":"دَرَّانٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (so accord. to the TT as from the M,) The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"fox."},{"kind":"text","text":"(M, K.)"}],"source_refs":["K"]},{"entry_id":"n12482","headword_ar":"دَرِنٌ","root":"drn","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoranu","text_ar":"اَدْرَنُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (M, TA,) applied to a garment,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dirty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filthy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, M, Msb, K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"defiled, polluted,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"smeared, with dirt,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"filth."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b2-  And, so applied,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Old and worn out;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"dariynN","text_ar":"دَرِينٌ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":". (K.) ―         -b3-  [Hence,]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadaAhu","text_ar":"يَدَاهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"daranaAtN biAlxayori","text_ar":"دَرَنَاتٌ بِالخَيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mina Alxayori","text_ar":"مِنَ الخَيْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":","},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His hands are worn out by beneficence;"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much used therein"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ayodiyhimo diraAnN","text_ar":"اَيْدِيهِمْ دِرَانٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Their hands are worn out"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereby]: and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"huwa darinu Alyadayoni","text_ar":"هُوَ دَرِنُ اليَدَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(tropical:)  ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He is worn out in respect of the hands"},{"kind":"text","text":"thereby]. (K, TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"darinapN","text_ar":"دَرِنَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"applied to a she-camel means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Mangy,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"scabby."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","M","Msb","K","TA"]}]}}